BlackBerry Users in Europe, India Face Issues

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   B r o w n i n g
-- 
2011-10-11T15:13:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/blackberry-users-in-europe-india-face-issues.html
BlackBerry users in  Europe , the
 Middle East ,  Africa ,  India ,  Brazil ,  Chile  and  Argentina  are
facing messaging and Internet browsing delays,  Research in
Motion Ltd. (RIM)  said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
